{"title":"公社好比一枝花（民歌）","authors":["逯?"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比一枝花（民歌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比一枝花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这枝鲜花党来插。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登封鲜花长的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯传遍千万家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民听到齐欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业实现机械化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业大学大家上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将来也要当专家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人听到蹦又跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂也要办学校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学知识都学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业技术也通啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生听到高歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤工俭学办工厂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各科常识都熟悉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亦工亦农是方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比一枝花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党来浇水培育它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这枝鲜花开的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福生活全靠它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔河南登封财政局　?乾搜集整理〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}